response.original_title: ROH & NJPW War Of The Worlds 2017: Toronto
response.overview: May 7th, 2017 :: Ring Of Honor and New Japan Pro Wrestling bring you the first night of the 2017 War Of The Worlds Tour live from Ted Reeve Arena in Toronto, Ontario, Canada. Matches include:  • Hiroshi Tanahashi & The Addiction (Christopher Daniels & Frankie Kazarian) vs. BULLET CLUB (Kenny Omega, Matt Jackson & Nick Jackson)  • Cody vs. Will Ospreay  • Jay Lethal vs. KUSHIDA  • Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI & Tetsuya Naito) vs. The Kingdom (Matt Taven & Vinny Marseglia)  • Bully Ray vs. Hangman Page vs. Punishment Martinez  • The Motor City Machine Guns (Alex Shelley & Chris Sabin) vs. The Rebellion (Caprice Coleman & Rhett Titus)  • Hirooki Goto vs. Shane Taylor  • Dalton Castle & The Boys (Boy 1 & Boy 2) vs. CHAOS (Beretta, Gedo & Rocky Romero)  • Silas Young & The Beer City Bruiser vs. The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) vs. Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL & SANADA)
response.title: ROH & NJPW War Of The Worlds 2017: Toronto
